data.title: Hostos CC Catalog
data.text: The Associate in Applied Science Degree in Digital Music will provide students with a strong foundation for music careers in business and industry. The curriculum is designed to provide students with the specialized knowledge, skills and hands-on experience now needed by creative professionals in addition to an awareness of industry opportunities. The curriculum also emphasizes the use of industry standard technology to help students plan, analyze and create music, sound and artistic productions.
